			"editorData": {
				"HowToTrigger": {
					"type": 23,
					"value": "1. Debug Book - Set Quest Flags - Act 2 - GLO Lifting the Curse - Halsin at camp with Spirit\r\n2. Debug Book - Set Quest Flags - Act 2 - GLO Lifting the Curse - Oliver fled to Town - this will teleport you to the plaze in the Town\r\n3. Approach Oliver, he will start a fight and summon some creatures.\r\n4. Teleport closer to him - he'll unsummon the creatures and start this dialog with you."
				},
